title: Nintendo Switch - Official Experience Trailer
description:
Take a look at the latest trailer for the Nintendo Switch highlighting what is possible on Nintendo's latest game console and how to expand your experience with the hybrid system. Explore the lands of Hyrule, get a workout in, or go online with the Nintendo Switch Online service. The Nintendo Switch is available now with the Nintendo Switch Lite, Nintendo Switch, and Nintendo Switch OLED.

title: Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising - Official 2B Gameplay Trailer
description:
Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising is a 2D multiplayer action fighting game developed by Cygames, Inc. and Arc System Works. Take a look at the latest trailer to get a glimpse at 2B, YoRHa No.2 Type B, from NieR: Automata in Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising. 2B is being added to the roster of Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising in February 2024.

title: Baldur's Gate 3 Guide: How to Solve the Defiled Temple Puzzle
description:
This video originally aired on August 8, 2023.

Fairly early on in your adventures in Baldur's Gate III, you might stumble on a puzzle inside the Defiled Crpyt. It's a floor puzzle that requires you to move the tiles to find its solution. In this video, we'll show you where to find the puzzle, and how to solve it!

title: Ghostrunner 2 Developers React to 56 Minute Speedrun
description:
Ghostrunner 2 is all about style and speed, and because of this, the series is a bonified hit with the speedrunning community. So ride along with the developers at One More Level as they watch and react to an incredible playthrough of their game from speedrunner Pasiflora.

title: Every IGN 10 of 2023
description:
What did IGN award a 10/10 score this year? Beware of spoilers ahead!

2023 has been packed with amazing games, movies, and TV shows, so we’ve put together a list of everything that we gave full marks. We gave out 17 whopping IGN 10/10 review scores! From shows like Succession, movies like Oppenheimer, and games like The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom and Baldur’s Gate 3, here’s everything we deemed worthy of being called a masterpiece this year.

#Gaming #Movies #TV

title: The Biggest Game Releases of January 2024
description:
Happy New Year! A new year brings new games, and while January might be a little lighter on releases, we're sure it'll pick up soon enough. Not to worry though, there's still a lot to look forward to this month. Between Tekken 8, Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth, and Prince of Persia: the Lost Crown, there should be enough to satisfy any type of gamer. So ride along with us as we list the biggest games to look forward to in January 2024!

#IGN #Gaming

title: GTA 5's Michael Has Some Advice For GTA 6's Lucia (Feat. Ned Luke) | GTFM
description:
Ned Luke’s the voice actor and model for Micheal in Grand Theft Auto 5. And according to him, Lucia in GTA 6 looks like "a badass". He tells us what we think of both Lucia and Jason, his relationship with Steven Ogg, and many other burning questions the GTA community has had. We dive deep into #GTA6 to discuss Ned’s reaction after seeing the #RockstarGames GTA 6 trailer. We discuss the new location of Leonida GTA 6 will explore, how he feels that Lucia, the GTA 6 actress should treat her fans, and how he believes the Grand Theft Auto 6 fans are what really makes the series special. The Grand Theft Auto 6 trailer has taken the internet by storm so who better to discuss than a former lead from GTA 5.

Find more from Ned Luke at
https://www.twitch.tv/nedluke
